<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 8; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
320 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Addiss, Justus J. Jr., 87, of North Hollywood, retired salesman. J. T. Oswald 
Mortuary, North Hollywood.  
</P>
<P>
 Bardakjian, Gadar O., 84, of Van Nuys, homemaker.Forest Lawn Mortuary, 
Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Bryan, Rosalie C., 55, of Granada Hills, assistant administrator for Villa 
Scalabrini Center. Forest Lawn Mortuary, Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Du Brock, Neal Lawrence, 70, of Studio City, theater producer. Forest Lawn 
Mortuary, Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Fernandez, Arthur M., 69, of Tarzana, manager for Movieland Motel. Forest Lawn 
Mortuary, Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Ferrante, Rose Elizabeth, 88, of Burbank, homemaker. The Valley Funeral Home, 
Burbank.  
