<HEADLINE>
<P>
INSTANT VIDEO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 How quickly can they turn around a video? Try eight days for ABC's "Richard M. 
Nixon: His Life and Times," hitting stores today. For $14.98 you get the April 
27 funeral, plus career highs and lows, including the Checkers speech, the 
Kennedy-Nixon debates, Vietnam, China and Watergate. 
</P>
