Monterey 227,550 -0.9 +30.0 Northern California 134,820 -1.2 +28.2 Northern 
wine country 185,880 -1.0 +24.9 Orange County 209,490 -4.5 +6.9 Palm 
Springs-low desert* 122,920 +1.0 +104.7 Riverside-San Bernardino 130,970 -3.2 
