interactive entertainment products in the United States and Britain in their 
first collaboration since the takeover of Paramount Communications Inc. Nynex 
Corp. and Viacom Inc. will develop video-on-demand services using the extensive 
libraries of film and television programming controlled by Viacom and 
Paramount. The companies will also work together to develop interactive 
versions of Viacom's cable networks, which include MTV, Nickelodeon and VH-1. 
