and treat him nice." With no better plan, she was willing to give it a try. 
</P>
<P>
 That night when her husband came home, blitzed as usual, she greeted him with, 
"I'm so happy to see you, baby. Why don't we go into the kitchen, have a bite 
to eat, talk awhile and then go to bed?" 
</P>
<P>
 "Why not?" he slurred. "I'm going to catch hell when I go home anyway." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Playboy, June, 1994 
