<P>
TWO TRABUCO HILLS VOLLEYBALL PLAYERS SIGN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Holly Falkenhagen of Trabuco Hills signed a letter of intent to play 
volleyball at Baylor, Trabuco Hills girls' volleyball Coach Gregg Swenson said. 
</P>
<P>
 Falkenhagen, an outside hitter, was first-team all-league last season. 
</P>
<P>
 Center Jenny Wilson, also of Trabuco Hills, has signed to play volleyball at 
the University of Denver, Swenson said. Wilson also was first-team all-league. 
