<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: MARKETING AND MEDIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Anne Michaud, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Fun for Kids Too: Taking the family on vacation this summer? International 
Care for Kids, a San Clemente company that supplies children activity kits to 
the hotel industry, has published a guide to family travel. 
</P>
<P>
 The Family & Travel directory lists more than 500 resorts that offer something 
special for families.It contains coupons and a toll-free number that will 
connect you to the resort of your choice. 
</P>
<P>
 "The company's experience consulting to the lodging industry has allowed it to 
monitor te family programs and promotions of more than 1,000 properties during 
the past four years," explains a promotional flyer for the directory. 
</P>
<P>
 The price -- a special through the end of May -- is $19 for the first copy and 
$9.99 for a second. 
</P>
