<P>
 "Chairman Arafat, our partner in a very difficult journey: We did it! 
</P>
<P>
 Once we had a dream before we had a map. Now we have a map and a dream 
together. 
</P>
<P>
 For almost half a century, we experienced blood and hatred, terror and war. 
Today, we declare that the conflict is over. We don't want to be the generals, 
the judges or the police of the Palestinian people. . . . Today, we welcome 
you, the Palestinian people, as neighbors." 
</P>
