7:30 p.m., and Sundays at 12:30, at El Mariachi Restaurant, 650 N. Tustin Ave., 
Orange. Friday through Sunday evenings the mariachis alternate with a Latin 
dance combo. Information: (714) 532-4001. Where to Catch Fiesta Fever 
</P>
